cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper deals with a machine learning problem of reducing the size of a training set while maintaining classification accuracy. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
